{"tid":2171551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"百警狂截查 青年堅持一人遊行","createTime":"2020-08-24T04:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T05:25:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"119a2201042bc120c88de41145cbca96cbe21a82","tid":2171551,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/TQ7SNCSQ55FYPGQXCQUH5XKO7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FTQ7SNCSQ55FYPGQXCQUH5XKO7I%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=f58885c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FTQ7SNCSQ55FYPGQXCQUH5XKO7I%2F&h=e2c7bafe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/TQ7SNCSQ55FYPGQXCQUH5XKO7I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n百警狂截查 青年堅持一人遊行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YHXzmLXsfMtBrZ7NhA27m4kJF34=/1737x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B67LIVK4U5EH7OFRHVUVPSSZCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYHXzmLXsfMtBrZ7NhA27m4kJF34%3D%2F1737x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB67LIVK4U5EH7OFRHVUVPSSZCE.jpg&h=d2705b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方昨在尖沙嘴大肆搜查年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】言論自由被打壓，用腳發聲越見危險。網民發起昨天「靜默喧嘩遊行」，惟未到預定出發時間，已有近百警員在起點尖沙嘴港鐵站出口內外佈防，並截停搜查路人，最終只有一人參與遊行。民權觀察成員沈偉男表示，在聚集開始前先打壓是警方一貫策略，質疑昨天即使無人聚集，警員仍在沒有合理懷疑下截查途人，侵犯私隱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察轟侵公眾私隱<br />\n<br />\n昨日是「香港之路」人鏈一周年，有網民發起「靜默喧嘩遊行」，下午一時半由尖沙嘴港鐵站A2出口出發至長沙灣政府合署，反。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n下午約2時，尖沙嘴仍未見有人群聚集，大量警員在彌敦道兩邊繼續戒備及截查途人，受查人士以年輕人為主。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n活動最後演變成「一人遊行」，下午3時響應網上號召到場的Adam表示，他一度向天高叫口號，即被警方截查，查問他到場意圖。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他其後一人步行至旺角警署對面，沿途曾有一人加入表示失望，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察成員沈偉男表示，在和平示威開始前先打壓已是近年警方的策略，昨天更進一步打壓「好多人都唔知嘅遊行」，質疑警方沒有合理懷疑截查途人，「相稱性原則，冇晒啦」，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HMhQQKTEQzaRlUQFOt3VbDuOHTo=/1281x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RQXH2BSMARB2NASZUOGLFMCOQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHMhQQKTEQzaRlUQFOt3VbDuOHTo%3D%2F1281x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRQXH2BSMARB2NASZUOGLFMCOQY.jpg&h=abb145ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■網民Adam到場高叫口號即被截查。"},{"pid":"00428bb9915b6a37250edefe474ffb98218af90b","tid":2171551,"uid":304431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真正手足"},{"pid":"4f306cc34b23d31c2ed10bb1c3a08db00221024c","tid":2171551,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00428bb9915b6a37250edefe474ffb98218af90b","tid":2171551,"uid":304431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真正手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05250087b2580c62028300386f91e7a6e971fe8","tid":2171551,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:31:49.000Z","msg":"一人遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhand joke"},{"pid":"761a142b61fa88b062809ae064649dfd78c727a6","tid":2171551,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"我行咗你都唔知啦"}]}